    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A–D: Habitus of Subniganda bambusoides sp. nov.: A. ♁ holotype from Tiger Hill, Darjeling, [India]; B. ♀ paratype from type locality; C. ♁ paratype from Arunachal Pradesh, [India]; D. ♁ paratype from Deorali Danda [Nepal]; E–F: Habitus of S. isolde (Schintlmeister, 1997): E. ♁ paratype from Mt. Fan-si-pan [Vietnam]; F. ♁ paratype from Guangxi [China]; G–H: Habitus of S. tristan (Schintlmeister, 1997): G. ♁ paratype from Yunnan [China]; H. ♁ holotype from Mt. Fan-si-pan [Vietnam]." ;
